lead_paragraph: Real Madrid ended La Liga leaders Barcelona's long unbeaten run with a 2-1 win in the Clasico, while Leicester City's fourth straight 1-0 win put them further atop the Premier League.

headline.print_headline: Real End Barca's Unbeaten Run, Leicester Win Again
